Neler Öğrendik

1. main() --- main methodu
2. print() ve println()
3. escape chars
4. primitive variables & String variable
5. Concatenation
6. Arithmetic Operators
7. Casting (implicit-Automatic-Widening, explicit-manual- narrowing)
